\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a96a89089a2b268140977f9f496fa5ab34f109","tid":889194,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DeUM8Rk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDeUM8Rk.png&h=70efc344&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17044305737cd0af8d363362a1a4eb533ef78847","tid":889194,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:54:55.000Z","msg":"啲人話香港係文化沙漠<br />\n而家咁睇根本係無稽之談<br />\n大家對文字嘅熱愛係超越世上任何一種情感<br />\n就算喺一個講女人嘅post都可以一張圖都無<br />\n單純咁去用文字嚟交流<br />\n好純真好超脫"},{"pid":"211dae9eb8d9a419e2f73df4c52d0c4f1dcdfb00","tid":889194,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"求你放過我啦好嗎？放學搭巴士返屋企想休息下個腦，啲阿嬸阿叔好喜歡大大聲講電話，已經夠折磨人<br />\n<br />\n今日！我隔離個阿叔用緊方言大大聲講電話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲方言講到粗口咁，翻譯唔到，點解有咁多個「系」字，好難聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n理系伍系既小既系 系毛<br />\n系牙理mo貢貢系奶<br />\n牙培貢理day<br />\n理伍貢理系培下之系<br />\n努貢momo系之尼牙<br />\n挑鋼 系妹理下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你講完未<br />\n<br />\n嘿系小既系毛 毛系麻<br />\n理矛貢貢秘 貢家度毛系既<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿叔終於落咗車，真係感謝主"},{"pid":"7df3a5a6e7b9eb5cf15dc9442dece9d71c00a411","tid":889194,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T11:58:08.000Z","msg":"當初上連登因為知你係連登仔 想了解連登仔嘅思維想同你有共同話題<br />\n而家分咗手 你亦無再上連登了<br />\n得返我日日係度上<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7f547c3923b701738122cc48e76837200e8631","tid":889194,"uid":179274,"l